Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] Moscow (DDP/ADN) -- Gerhard Frey, leader of the 
right-wing extremist German People's Union (DVU), is expected to 
arrive in Moscow today to hold talks with Vladimir Zhirinovskiy, 
