They said Frey and Zhirinovskiy intend to hold a joint news 
conference tomorrow at the State Duma building. 
  Zhirinovskiy only met Frey at the end of December during a 
short stopover in Munich. Zhirinovskiy and Frey have had close 
contacts for years. [passage omitted] 

