<F P=100> ANNEX </F>
<F P=101> International Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Eureka Announces Closer Ties With Israel </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BR1801105494 Brussels EUROPE in English 15 Jan 94--FOR 
OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR1801105494 </F>
<F P=104>  Brussels EUROPE </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed article: "Eureka Supports Closer Cooperation </F>
With Israel"; as released by Brussels TEXTLINE database] 
  [Text] The Norwegian Presidency of Eureka [European 
Research Initiative] has announced that closer cooperation with 
Israel (which has not asked to become a member) was decided 
during a meeting of the top-level group in December. Eureka has 
21 members (20 plus the European Commission). 

</TEXT>

