<H3> <TI>   Mojahidin Group Denies Link to Embassy Attack </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BR2601100194 Bern ATSA/SDAA in French 1534 GMT 25 Jan 
94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR2601100194 </F>
<F P=104>  Bern ATSA/SDAA </F>


