<F P=100> TURKEY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Four Security Officials, 21 `Terrorists' Killed </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA2701193094 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1700 
GMT 27 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2701193094 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Turkish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over still of regional map] </F>
  [Text] Twenty-one terrorists have been killed in clashes 
that erupted between terrorists and security forces near 
Tunceli's Mazgirt District and Bingol's Genc District. Four 
security officials were martyred during the clashes. 
  According to a statement issued by the State of Emergency 
Region Governor's Office, a terrorist surrendered in Batman. 

</TEXT>

